# Python Bytecode and Caching
# ==========================================
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so

# ==========================================
# Virtual Environments
# ==========================================
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
ActiveEnv/

# ==========================================
